Default NAMED configuration files are:

  named.conf
  acl-named.conf
  channels-named.conf
  controls-named.conf
  local-named.conf
  masters-named.conf
  options-named.conf
  servers-named.conf
  statistics-named.conf
  trusted-keys-named.conf

For multiple instances of bind daemons, preface named.conf-class filename
with something like 'dmz-', 'int-', 'public-', 'red-', or 'white-'.

Zone filename begin with 'zone.'

View filename begin with 'view.'
